at.ac.tuwien.infosys.g2021.daemon

Class Gatherer

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.ac.tuwien.infosys.g2021.daemon.ValueChangeProducer
      • at.ac.tuwien.infosys.g2021.daemon.Gatherer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ActorGatherer, DummyGatherer, SensorGatherer, TestGatherer

    abstract class Gatherer
extends ValueChangeProducer
    A gatherer represents a single value of a hardware interface. This may be an actor or a sensor. Gatherers are identified by a gatherer configuration. For a single hardware value, there exists only a single gatherer.
